Welcome to the national
book festival.

00:00:04.310 --> 00:00:05.610
Are you guys excited?

00:00:05.610 --> 00:00:10.730
Come on. I am here to
introduce Chris Grabenstein,

00:00:10.730 --> 00:00:13.680
who is a number one New York
Times bestselling author

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:17.880
from the action-filled Escape
from Mr. Lemoncello's Library.

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:19.420
He has several more
books in the series,

00:00:19.420 --> 00:00:22.370
which I'm sure you all are
aware, and he also has Welcome

00:00:22.370 --> 00:00:25.290
to the Wonderland Series, and
he's cowritten numerous books

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:28.780
with James Patterson like
I Funny and Jacky Ha-Ha.

00:00:28.780 --> 00:00:30.320
Well see, there we go.

00:00:30.320 --> 00:00:32.470
