They're always a
little bit different.

00:06:53.860 --> 00:06:55.160
Read the book please.

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:57.730
And that was kind of fun
because it starred this kid,

00:06:57.730 --> 00:07:01.400
Casey Simpson, who stars in that
Nickelodeon show Ricky Dickey

00:07:01.400 --> 00:07:03.030
Donkey Dorky Dooky--

00:07:03.030 --> 00:07:05.040
[ Inaudible Comment ]

