And also Brianna Edie was
in the show, and I got to go

00:07:10.490 --> 00:07:15.060
out to Hollywood and got to
be on the set with everybody.

00:07:15.060 --> 00:07:16.360
And it was a lot of fun.

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:17.660
There were great actors.

00:07:17.660 --> 00:07:19.100
And then I got to go
to the movie premiere

00:07:19.100 --> 00:07:20.990
